Popular Nollywood child star-turned-billionaire wife Regina Daniels has been hospitalised once again for the third time in a span of few weeks. In May, The Nation had reported the actress was back to the hospital weeks after she underwent successful surgery in April for an undisclosed ailment. However, the actress revealed on her social media page on Tuesday that she’s back to the hospital and is quite sad about it. Sharing a photo of her bandaged wrist with plaster on and several medical items scattered around, the mother of one captioned post: “Man down again” accompanied with a sad emoji.